This repository contains the code and slides for a presentation about using Groovy to test Java code.

Presentation:
The original presentation is in Keynote, but there is an exported PowerPoint deck if you do not have Keynote.

Tools needed:
  Git 
  Groovy
  Java
  Gradle

Install Tools:
  On Mac OS X:
    If you do not have Homebrew install it (https://github.com/mxcl/homebrew)
    Git: brew install git
    Groovy: brew install groovy
    Java: brew install java
    Gradle: brew install gradle

Run Build:
  gradle build
  the unit test reports are in:  build/reports/tests
